OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772806276
OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,FThe organiser of a vigil held to mark
OL,8,Ffive years since the murder of Sarah
OL,9,FEverard said "much more needs to be
OL,10,Fdone" for women to feel safe and to
OL,11,Ftackle violence against women and
OL,12,Fgirls.
OL,14,FMs Everard, a 33-year-old marketing
OL,15,Fexecutive, was abducted, raped and
OL,16,Fmurdered by a serving Metropolitan
OL,17,FPolice officer as she walked home from
OL,18,Fa friend's house in south London on
OL,19,FMarch 3 2021.
OL,26,@qD@NOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772806276
OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,FHe had used his status to trick her
OL,8,Finto thinking he could arrest her for
OL,9,Fbreaking Covid-19 lockdown rules.
OL,11,FA vigil was held in Clapham Common,
OL,12,Fsouth London, on Tuesday evening,
OL,13,Fclose to where Ms Everard was abducted.
OL,15,FKlara Fine, 29, who works at the
OL,16,Fevent's organiser Best of Clapham,
OL,17,Ftold the Press Association: "If a lone
OL,18,Fpoliceman came up to me and asked me
OL,19,Fto get into his car I would tell him
OL,20,Fto 'f' off, to be honest.
OL,26,@yD@]OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772806276
OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, that's the sad
OL,8,Freality, and I think that violence
OL,9,Fagainst women in general starts from
OL,10,Fschool, school boys.
OL,12,F"Much more needs to be done on a
OL,13,Fnational level.
OL,15,F"At the moment it just feels like it's
OL,16,Fsmaller communities who are providing
OL,17,Fsafe spaces and supporting each other
OL,18,Fand charities, and it's just really
OL,19,Fnot good enough."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772806276
OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,FAbout 100 people gathered at the vigil
OL,8,Fto lay flowers, observe a minute of
OL,9,Fsilence and remember Ms Everard
OL,10,Ftogether.
OL,12,FAfter thanking people for attending,
OL,13,FMs Fine told the crowd: "We're here
OL,14,Fthis evening to remember her because
OL,15,Fshe deserves to be remembered.
OL,26,@uD@YOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772806276
OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,F"We remember her not as a headline,
OL,8,Fnot as a case, not as a moment in the
OL,9,Fnews cycle, but as Sarah, a daughter,
OL,10,Fa friend, a woman with plans, laughter
OL,11,Fand the future ahead of her, cruelly
OL,12,Ftaken away."
OL,14,FJoanna Reynolds, who was ward
OL,15,Fcouncillor for Clapham Common at the
OL,16,Ftime of Ms Everard's murder five years
OL,17,Fago, said: "We do need to reclaim the
OL,18,Fstreets, reclaim the night.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@LO]yD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772806276
OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,F"It's important that, for all of us
OL,8,Fand for our children and for any girls
OL,9,Fthat are growing, that we make sure
OL,10,Fthat it's not just about us women,
OL,11,Fit's about the men here.
OL,13,F"We need to make sure that they and
OL,14,Fthe boys growing up understand how
OL,15,Fthey should treat the women in their
OL,16,Flives and the women that they see on
OL,17,Fthe streets."
OL,19,FShe added: "I cannot imagine what it
OL,20,Fwas like for Sarah, at the moment she
OL,21,Fgot into that car.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@MO]{D@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772806276
OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,F"Or for her family, and particularly
OL,8,Fher parents, how they must have felt
OL,9,Fduring that time."
OL,11,FOrganised by the local news page Best
OL,12,Fof Clapham, the vigil also raised
OL,13,Ffunds for London-based charity Solace
OL,14,FWomen's Aid, which supports women and
OL,15,Fchildren affected by domestic abuse
OL,16,Fand sexual violence.
OL,18,FAsked why she attended the vigil, Izzy
OL,19,FAirey, 24, said: "I live locally and I
OL,20,Fcome to the park often.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@RO]{D@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772806276
OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,F"I would never walk here alone at
OL,8,Fnight, or like if I was to go home
OL,9,Fthrough here in dark I'd be like on a
OL,10,Fbike and like zooming through.
OL,12,F"So holding the vigil here, with a lot
OL,13,Fof women, and coming together
OL,14,Fbasically to commemorate her, is
OL,15,Factually super powerful."
OL,17,FThe student, from Brixton, south
OL,18,FLondon, added: "Parks at night are
OL,19,Fobviously super dangerous, but the
OL,20,Fdaily reality for women is that they
OL,21,Fhave to just be careful."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@YO]zD@POU}D@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
