OL,3,CSarah Everard vigil organiser says
OL,4,C'much more' needs doing for women to
OL,5,Cbe safe
OL,7,FSpeaking of the police, she said:
OL,8,F"You'd hope that they would listen to
OL,9,Fyou, but I guess in reality I don't
OL,10,Freally know.
OL,12,F"I feel like I would probably contact
OL,13,Fmy family before I call the police
OL,14,Fprobably, because I think it's
OL,15,Fintimidating."
OL,17,FMs Everard's mother Susan said her
OL,18,Fdaughter had "added to the beauty of
OL,19,Fthe world" in a tribute piece for
OL,20,FBritish Vogue.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUwD@NO]zD@NOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
